  "title": "Production Supervisor",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Well Established Company </strong></li><li><strong>Salary $2500 - $3000 + OT + Allowance + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li><li><strong>Working Location : East</strong></li><li><strong>Working hours : Permanent Night Shift (8pm to 8am)</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Responsible for overseeing the production process to ensure that products are manufactured efficiently, safely, and within quality standards</li><li><strong>Monitor and oversee the daily production activities in the injection moulding area </strong></li><li>Ensure that production schedules are met, and that machines are operating at optimal capacity</li><li><strong>Oversee the setup, operation, and maintenance of injection moulding machines</strong></li><li>Identify and resolve any issues that arise during production, such as machine malfunctions or quality defects</li><li><strong>Mould set-up (Single/Double Colour)</strong></li><li>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Minimum GCE ‘O’ Level / Nitec / Diploma in Quality Assurance or equivalent with minimum 2 years’ experience in Plastics Injection (Single/Double Colour)</strong></li></ul><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)</p><p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
